#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1336
msgid ""
"Which PayPal buttons (e.g. Pay Later, Venmo, SEPA, iDEAL, Mercado Pago, "
"Bancontact, etc.) will appear?"
msgstr ""
"Butang PayPal mana (cth. Bayar Kemudian, Venmo, SEPA, iDEAL, Mercado Pago, "
"Bancontact, dll.) akan dipaparkan?"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1340
msgid ""
"The PayPal buttons are shown automatically based on several factors, "
"including:"
msgstr ""
"Butang PayPal dipaparkan secara automatik berdasarkan beberapa faktor, "
"termasuk:"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1342
msgid "The buyer’s country"
msgstr "Negara pembeli"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1343
msgid "Their device type"
msgstr "Jenis peranti mereka"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1344
msgid "The funding sources they’ve enabled"
msgstr "Sumber pembiayaan yang telah mereka aktifkan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1346
msgid ""
"As a result, each buyer may see a different set of buttons. Pay Later "
"options vary by country and may display different buttons."
msgstr ""
"Hasilnya, setiap pembeli mungkin melihat set butang yang berbeza. Pilihan "
"Bayar Kemudian berbeza mengikut negara dan mungkin memaparkan butang yang "
"berbeza."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1352
msgid "How can I hide specific PayPal buttons?"
msgstr "Bagaimana saya boleh menyembunyikan butang PayPal tertentu?"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1356
msgid ""
"By default, all PayPal buttons are enabled. To hide specific buttons, use "
"the <strong>Disable Specific Payment Buttons</strong> option."
msgstr ""
"Secara lalai, semua butang PayPal diaktifkan. Untuk menyembunyikan butang "
"tertentu, gunakan pilihan <strong>Nyahaktifkan Butang Pembayaran "
"Tertentu</strong>."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1357
msgid "Example: To hide the Pay Later button on the Checkout Page:"
msgstr ""
"Contoh: Untuk menyembunyikan butang Bayar Kemudian di Halaman Pembayaran:"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1359
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1376
msgid "Go to <strong>PayPal Settings</strong> > Checkout Page"
msgstr "Pergi ke <strong>Tetapan PayPal</strong> > Halaman Pembayaran"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1360
msgid "Find the <strong>Disable Specific Payment Buttons</strong> setting."
msgstr ""
"Cari tetapan <strong>Nyahaktifkan Butang Pembayaran Tertentu</strong>."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1361
msgid "Select <strong>Pay Later</strong> from the dropdown list."
msgstr "Pilih <strong>Bayar Kemudian</strong> dari senarai juntai bawah."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1362
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1378
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1384
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1401
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1407
msgid "Click <strong>Save Changes</strong>."
msgstr "Klik <strong>Simpan Perubahan</strong>."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1369
msgid "How can I show only the \"PayPal\" button on the Checkout page?"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana saya boleh memaparkan hanya butang \"PayPal\" di halaman "
"Pembayaran?"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1373
msgid ""
"To display only the \"PayPal\" button on the Checkout page, follow these "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memaparkan hanya butang \"PayPal\" di halaman Pembayaran, ikuti "
"langkah-langkah ini:"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1374
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1397
msgid "Step 1: Update PayPal Settings"
msgstr "Langkah 1: Kemas kini Tetapan PayPal"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1377
msgid ""
"Under <strong>Disable Specific Payment Buttons</strong>, select "
"<strong>Credit or Debit Card</strong> and any other methods you want to "
"hide."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah <strong>Nyahaktifkan Butang Pembayaran Tertentu</strong>, pilih "
"<strong>Kad Kredit atau Debit</strong> dan mana-mana kaedah lain yang anda "
"mahu sembunyikan."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-gateway.php:1380
