#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1882
msgid ""
"Choose whether you wish to capture funds immediately or authorize payment "
"only."
msgstr ""
"Pilih sama ada anda mahu menangkap dana serta-merta atau membenarkan "
"pembayaran sahaja."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1886
msgid "Capture"
msgstr "Tangkap"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1887
msgid "Authorize"
msgstr "Benarkan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1891
msgid "Brand Name"
msgstr "Nama Jenama"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1893
msgid ""
"This controls what users see as the brand / company name on PayPal review "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"Ini mengawal apa yang pengguna lihat sebagai nama jenama / syarikat pada "
"halaman semakan PayPal."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1898
msgid "Landing Page"
msgstr "Halaman Pendaratan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1901
msgid ""
"The type of landing page to show on the PayPal site for customer checkout. "
"PayPal Account Optional must be checked for this option to be used."
msgstr ""
"Jenis halaman pendaratan untuk ditunjukkan di laman PayPal untuk pembayaran "
"pelanggan. PayPal Account Optional mesti ditandakan untuk pilihan ini "
"digunakan."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1902
msgid "Login"
msgstr "Log Masuk"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1903
msgid "Billing"
msgstr "Pengebilan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1904
msgid "No Preference"
msgstr "Tiada Keutamaan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1909
msgid "Instant Payments "
msgstr "Pembayaran Segera "

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1913
msgid ""
"If you enable this setting, PayPal will be instructed not to allow the buyer"
" to use funding sources that take additional time to complete (for example, "
"eChecks). Instead, the buyer will be required to use an instant funding "
"source, such as an instant transfer, a credit/debit card, or PayPal Credit."
msgstr ""
"Jika anda mengaktifkan tetapan ini, PayPal akan diarahkan untuk tidak "
"membenarkan pembeli menggunakan sumber pembiayaan yang mengambil masa "
"tambahan untuk diselesaikan (contohnya, eCek). Sebaliknya, pembeli akan "
"dikehendaki menggunakan sumber pembiayaan segera, seperti pemindahan segera,"
" kad kredit/debit, atau PayPal Credit."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1916
msgid "Require Instant Payment"
msgstr "Memerlukan Pembayaran Segera"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1919
msgid "Billing Address"
msgstr "Alamat Pengebilan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1920
msgid "Use PayPal Shipping Address as Billing"
msgstr "Gunakan Alamat Penghantaran PayPal sebagai Pengebilan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1921
msgid ""
"If the billing address is empty and PayPal provides a shipping address, the "
"order will use the shipping address as the billing address."
msgstr ""
"Jika alamat pengebilan kosong dan PayPal menyediakan alamat penghantaran, "
"pesanan akan menggunakan alamat penghantaran sebagai alamat pengebilan."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1927
msgid "Send Item Details"
msgstr "Hantar Butiran Item"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1928
msgid "Send line item details to PayPal"
msgstr "Hantar butiran item baris ke PayPal"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1930
msgid ""
"Include all line item details in the payment request to PayPal so that they "
"can be seen from the PayPal transaction details page."
msgstr ""
"Sertakan semua butiran item baris dalam permintaan pembayaran ke PayPal "
"supaya ia boleh dilihat dari halaman butiran transaksi PayPal."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1934
msgid "Order Review Page"
msgstr "Halaman Semakan Pesanan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1935
msgid "Skip Order Review Page"
msgstr "Langkau Halaman Semakan Pesanan"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1937
msgid ""
"Payments from the Product or Cart page skip the review step and go straight "
"to the Thank You page."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran dari halaman Produk atau Troli melangkau langkah semakan dan "
"terus ke halaman Terima Kasih."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1944
msgid "Invoice prefix"
msgstr "Awalan invois"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1946
msgid ""
"Please enter a prefix for your invoice numbers. If you use your PayPal "
"account for multiple stores ensure this prefix is unique as PayPal will not "
"allow orders with the same invoice number."
msgstr ""
"Sila masukkan awalan untuk nombor invois anda. Jika anda menggunakan akaun "
"PayPal anda untuk beberapa kedai pastikan awalan ini unik kerana PayPal "
"tidak akan membenarkan pesanan dengan nombor invois yang sama."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1951
msgid "Credit Card Statement Name"
msgstr "Nama Penyata Kad Kredit"

